{"tid":825174,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)強國巨齒鯊 極度深寒 深海圓疑 撕裂地平線","createTime":"2018-09-17T11:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T20:14:41.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a836cf1d784a30b110fbccbfd86a081e6c040e32","tid":825174,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=z1IDjD4uVzwJD3VvrO13UAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=936c954b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=z1IDjD4uVzwJD3VvrO13UAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0553d8d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=z1IDjD4uVzwJD3VvrO13UAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6868c34f\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/29/The_Meg_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F29%2FThe_Meg_Poster.jpg&h=cb1a0f6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bd/Deep_rising_ver3.jpg/220px-Deep_rising_ver3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2Fb%2Fbd%2FDeep_rising_ver3.jpg%2F220px-Deep_rising_ver3.jpg&h=799b686c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/danlkaelb/2dfda9d8fed9218fd6688186bb82b237.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fdanlkaelb%2F2dfda9d8fed9218fd6688186bb82b237.jpg&h=ebadb0ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/8c/Event_horizon_ver1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F8c%2FEvent_horizon_ver1.jpg&h=368d580f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.電影《巨齒鯊》改編自紐約時報暢銷作家 史蒂芬艾騰（Steve Alten）的同名科幻小說，帶領觀眾下沉到太平洋最深處，體驗深海的窒息恐懼。角色主要設定居住在一艘深海潛艇裡，從事研究工作，卻突遭 75 英尺長的史前巨鯊攻擊、威脅生命，他們將不顧一切與牠對戰<br />\n<br />\n2.一艘遊輪被貪婪噬血的怪物所盤據，受僱走私的約翰費尼根（崔特威廉斯飾）領隊的「塞班號」恰巧接近這艘郵輪，他的船員包括凱文歐康諾飾及大副萊拉（伍娜戴蒙飾）。當費尼根將他破損的「塞班號」停泊在「亞格遠征號」旁並攀爬上船時，發現處處都是遊輪遭到襲擊的痕跡，甲板上到處都是血，空氣凝重，靜默中充滿詭譎的氣氛..<br />\n<br />\n3.科學小組利用高科技的實驗艇深入海底進行探測，他們進入太空船後，發現了一個『2048年美國製造』的字樣，證明了這是艘未來的太空船，曾經歷時空旅行來到此地，船內部有一個巨大而怪異的球狀體，當他們先後進入這球狀體後，人人都產生了詭異的反應與幻象..<br />\n<br />\n4.西元2040年，政府秘密製造的「Event Horizon號」太空船，要以新研發的重力驅動系統，製造出人造黑洞以進行時空重疊，可瞬間跳躍至數光年甚至數千光年以外之地，用來縮短太空探索時間的新科技。但該船在啟動首次的重力跳躍後，便一去不回，直到2047年才重新現身於海王星附近<br />\n<br />\n8 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  *巨齒鯊係北韓流出版<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=z1IDjD4uVzwJD3VvrO13UAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=76bdd847\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=z1IDjD4uVzwJD3VvrO13UAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=c084a2fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d453987d704a61d263375411e9fff3246dc9650e","tid":825174,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da48452fd60e3ca9ad520351d42f01a9725dcb4e","tid":825174,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"改9 15PM"},{"pid":"d5b5808a8106421ae9182be364bc977d5f2747bf","tid":825174,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0acedb94788c77a9c3311085d3f417caeedf5b9","tid":825174,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b533303718575d328fd33998063be899e94ed54f","tid":825174,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c25a1b4c0819134089be5f687fad311f4592b56","tid":825174,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdff5020a985347c0a15d164ecf9c832670a100c","tid":825174,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci